verbose_text: The field trials were conducted on-farm in the 2013 cropping season at Kpataribogu {9degrees58 ' N, 0degrees40 ' W; 172 m above sea level (masl)} in the Karaga District (southern Guinea savanna, SGS) and at Bundunia (10degrees51 ' N, 1degrees04 ' W; 185 masl) in the Kassena-Nankana East Municipal (northern Guinea savanna, NGS) of northern Ghana.
